title: Jalen Ramsey and the All-in Rams, Trade Predictions, and Cowboys-Eagles | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Seven players tie up 60 percent of the Rams' cap space, and now they have traded for Jalen Ramsey. Is this going to work? (2:10) Then, other superstar players that could move before the trade deadline (13:15), before we get to our biggest three games of the week, headlined by the Cowboys vs. the Eagles (28:15); talk about Kliff Kingsbury’s promising adjustments in his first season as a head coach; and preview 'Thursday Night Football' (41:15).
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
